    "description": "<u>Overview</u><br><br>Crazy Poker is an exciting take on the popular game of poker.  The object of the game is to score points by making poker hands across a number of rounds.<br><br><u>Gameplay</u><br><br>In Crazy Poker you deal cards to one of three hands, trying to make the best poker hands possible.  Once a card is placed it cannot be moved, which means you have to find a balance between chasing the high scoring hands and playing safe to ensure that you actually bank some points.<br><br>Games are played across a number of rounds and extra rounds are awarded based upon your score.<br><br>Your challenge awaits...",
